metadata.description:
<Leaderboard>

This series of ten photographs <Leaderboard> are a love letter I wanted to live on the blockchain for an eternity - fuck it, why not?

This shoot is from such a chaotic and challenging time of transformation in my life - these images capture a lot more to me than something pretty - there's a lot of pain too.  Having people in my life to look up to and be inspired by has always helped me survive riding this rocket. 

I hope these images translate the duality of our being, and how complicated the world is... hold onto the people who see you with all your heart, bc if you've seen GDT's Pinocchio, you'd know it's kind of all we have, and it's v fleeting.

ty for seeing 
the fractal 
through the trees  
it's your reflection, after all

If you're top of the leaderboard, you know who you are...
